SubjectAdministrator (ON) multiple July 1 - August 31, 2011
PrecisAppointment to serve as ADMINISTRATOR of the Government of Ontario the Hon. HEATHER J. SMITH from July 1-3, 2011, inclusive, and from August 8-31, 2011, inclusive; the Hon. DENNIS R. O'CONNOR from July 4-31, 2011, inclusive; and the Hon. MICHAEL J. MOLDAVER from August 1-7, 2011, inclusive.
